Apeface nealt over the side of the huge secret launch site that was now
exposed. He knew the Council enjoyed the relay of information he sent
them, as they needed to get going. When he heard the explosions, he came
right away, the Autobots were so busy, they didnt notice him crouch and
take in the info. He stood up, and streched out his arms, they made a
gurgling noise of oil popping. He then transformed into his Ape mode,
and leapt gracefully from one rooftop, to another, then leapt down, and
grabbed ahold of some steel gurders, to quietly move himself down. Once
at the ground, he ran a few streets down, then transformed into his jet
mode, and took off towards Predacon territory.
